      "content": "oh wow, i didnt realize u were that certain about it. i thought u were gonna give me the \"it's complicated\" answer like before. so u basically believe that more social support is just bad for the economy because it stops people from working? is there any real evidence that accounts for other stuff like automation or just people getting older?",
